[Scene01]

Leaving Teeka to lead the ground assault, Bob entered the BioMech tower. His final
battle was just beginning and all that stood between him and his ultimate confrontation
with Galdov were the floors of the tower and the scores of enemy forces that
occupied them.

[Scene02]

Galdov patiently awaited Bob's arrival on the roof where the two would fight for
the fate of the Blobs and the planet that was their home. But with the evil Biomech 
leader's bases destroyed and his forces in tatters Bob knew Galdov now had little
to lose. And that would make him more dangerous than ever...

[END]
